``` mermaid
graph TD
A[Start] --> B[Define Question class]
B --> C[Define Quiz class]
C --> D[Add questions to Quiz]
D --> E[Start Quiz]
E --> F[Display first question]
F --> G[Ask user for answer]
G --> H{Check answer}
H -- Correct --> I[Update score]
I --> J[Display next question]
J --> F
H -- incorrect --> I
J -- Last question --> K[Display user score]
K -->L[End]


```